OL,3,CWhat happens now as former Labour MP
OL,4,CMike Amesbury jailed?
OL,6,FA former Labour MP is facing the
OL,7,Fpossibility of losing his seat after
OL,8,Fhe was jailed for punching a
OL,9,Fconstituent.
OL,11,FMike Amesbury, was handed 10 weeks in
OL,12,Fprison after he admitted assaulting 45-
OL,13,Fyear-old Paul Fellows in Main Street
OL,14,Fin Frodsham, Cheshire, in the early
OL,15,Fhours of 26 October.
OL,17,FThe MP, who represents Runcorn and
OL,18,FHelsby, has been sitting as an
OL,19,Findependent since he was suspended
OL,20,Ffrom the Labour Party following his
OL,21,Farrest.
