OL,3,CWhat happens now as former Labour MP
OL,4,CMike Amesbury jailed?
OL,6,FHis jail term means he could now lose
OL,7,Fhis seat in the Commons after he was
OL,8,Fleft liable to the recall process,
OL,9,Fwhich would trigger a by-election if
OL,10,F10% of registered voters in his seat
OL,11,Fsign a petition calling for it.
OL,13,FWhat is a recall petition?
OL,15,F'Recall petitions' are used to trigger
OL,16,Fan election to remove an MP from their
OL,17,Frole, away from scheduled elections.
OL,19,FIn the UK, a recall can only be
OL,20,Fstarted under specific circumstances:
