OL,3,CWhat happens now as former Labour MP
OL,4,CMike Amesbury jailed?
OL,6,FOnce one of the conditions has been
OL,7,Fmet, all eligible voters within a
OL,8,Fconstituency can go to a maximum of 10
OL,9,Flocations to sign the petition.
OL,11,FThose locations will remain open for a
OL,12,Fduration of six weeks.
OL,14,FVoters will sign a sheet, and place it
OL,15,Fin a sealed ballot box, similar to
OL,16,Fpolling stations during a general
OL,17,Felection.
OL,19,FThe counting of signing sheets are
OL,20,Falso completed in a similar way to
OL,21,Fballot papers.
