OL,3,CWhat happens now as former Labour MP
OL,4,CMike Amesbury jailed?
OL,6,FIf at least 10% of the registered
OL,7,Felectorate sign the petition, then the
OL,8,Fseat becomes vacant which would
OL,9,Ftrigger a by-election.
OL,11,FFollowing the sentence, the Labour
OL,12,FParty said his constituency residents
OL,13,F"deserved better", hinting at a
OL,14,Fpossible by-election.
OL,16,FA spokesperson said: "The Labour Party
OL,17,Ftook swift action following Mike
OL,18,FAmesbury's completely unacceptable
OL,19,Factions and he is no longer a Labour
OL,20,FMP or a member of the Labour Party.
