OL,3,CWhat happens now as former Labour MP
OL,4,CMike Amesbury jailed?
OL,6,F"It is right that Mr Amesbury pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty and has now been sentenced.
OL,9,F"Local residents in the Runcorn and
OL,10,FHelsby constituency deserved better
OL,11,Fand we look forward to them getting
OL,12,Fthe representation they deserve in the
OL,13,Ffuture with a new Labour MP."
OL,15,FThe Reform UK party chairman Zia Yusuf
OL,16,Falso called for Amesbury to stand down
OL,17,Fso a by-election could be held.
